{
  "stem": "20021.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not in the house, because that would have been too suspicious.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Both the neighbors and the landlady would have suspected, here, what's this man hiding here?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was the biggest problem, what to do with myself during the whole day, you see?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What did you know or hear about the Warsaw ghetto, living--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I was-- as I was traveling in the trolley, which was packed, as the trolley was passing by certain streets, you could hear shots from the ghetto, sporadic like gunshots, not put-put-put like from a machine gun, but a gunshot here, and then later another gunshot, a gunshot, a gunshot.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the people we're talking about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now true, the comments were terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This unnerved me so much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, in Poland, the-- the Poles used their standard jokes about Jews, mostly about the fact that they're cowards and that they never held a rifle in their hands, you know, and this type of stuff.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Those were pre-1939 pre-war jokes about Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they kept repeating the same jokes, how a Jew is handling a rifle, how a Jew is shooting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Here is such a heroic effort, people, the only people who were standing the German army, the Poles didn't dare do that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I mean, in Europe practically at that point, including France and everybody else, nobody stood up to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody surrendered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And here's a group of people who dare to do that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I remember that vividly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Another thing which I remember is at one point as I was walking the streets, I arrived at a corner where there I saw of group of Polish women.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were very excited.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I come close, and I-- it's a crowd.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
